# assets/references/ -- local-only home for reference material (read-only, never a build input).
#
# An official place to keep project-folder references and source clones used while working on this
# project -- e.g. the pret/pokered disassembly, or the GitHub sources credited in
# projects/db/assets/data/credits.json -- so they have a known home and can be dropped back here if
# they ever get deleted, then referenced until they do.
#
# NONE of the contents are version-controlled (they can be large and are not ours to ship); only
# this .gitignore is tracked, which is what keeps the otherwise-empty folder in the repo.
*
!.gitignore
